{"tid":1971534,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人應承我：唔好再租機做台主","createTime":"2020-04-14T03:31:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T03:31:38.000Z","uid":192047,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1a8383c99b5a609cc7171824c8291c8d1aede0b0","tid":1971534,"uid":192047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T03:31:38.000Z","msg":"大J哥哥講得好啱<br />\n<br />\n有班人（屎陣營）不停拍片話做台主正 賺到錢<br />\n<br />\n吸引其他人去租機 4000~8000一個月租<br />\n<br />\n結果做晒水魚 因為根本cover唔到個租金<br />\n<br />\n其實大J哥哥根本冇指明邊個 只係提我哋職場陷阱<br />\n<br />\n結果屎陣營對號入座 仲成班黑社會圍威喂咁 狙擊大J哥哥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}